title: GoTo seeks to buck tech sector slump with $1.1 billion Indonesia IPO - Economic Times
content: GoTo seeks to buck tech sector slump with $1.1 billion Indonesia IPO  Economic Times
description: GoTo is selling 4% in shares with most taken up by funds. Backed by names such as SoftBank Group Corp's Vision Fund 1, Alibaba Group Holding Ltd and the Abu Dhabi Investment Authority, GoTo is also broadening its investor base by allocating shares to 600,000 drivers.
